---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <style>
    .page-header {
      position: relative;
      padding: 3rem 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #4a4a4a;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .page-header {
        padding: 4rem 0 5rem 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
        border-left-width: 6px;
      }
    }

    .page-header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -3px;
      top: 0;
      width: 2px;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8a8a8a 0%, #4a4a4a 100%);
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
      }
    }

    .page-header .subtitle {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .page-header .subtitle {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
    }

    .intro-section {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .intro-section {
        grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
      }
    }

    .profile-image {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 20%;
      border: 3px solid #d0d0d0;
      filter: grayscale(20%);
      justify-self: start;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .profile-image {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .profile-image {
        border-color: #505050;
      }
    }

    .intro-text {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .section-header {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: #666;
      margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem 0;
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .section-header {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        margin: 4rem 0 2rem 0;
        padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .section-header {
        color: #999;
        border-bottom-color: #404040;
      }
    }

    .contact-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .contact-list li {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin: 0.75rem 0;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .contact-list li::before {
      content: '>';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #888;
    }

    .content-section {
      max-width: 50rem;
    }

    .content-section p {
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }
  </style>

  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Software Engineer / Based in Portugal</p>
  </header>

  <div class="intro-section">
    <img
      src="/about/miguelMota.jpeg"
      alt="Miguel Mota"
      class="profile-image"
    />
    <p class="intro-text">
      My name is Miguel. I'm a Computer Science graduate, and I've lived and worked in various
      countries in Western Europe over the last decade. I like to take on various projects to
      explore programming languages and frameworks. Some of my past projects ranged from topics
      such as data science, fintech, audio/video processing, and game development. In recent
      years, my main focus has been on Python-based projects, and it's been quite a ride so far!
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="content-section">
    <p>
      Outside software development, I enjoy spending time with my family, playing board games,
      watching TV shows, and reading a good book.
    </p>

    <h2 class="section-header">My Projects</h2>
    <p>
      I work on a few pet projects in my spare time, mostly in the fintech space.
      Check out my <a href="/projects">projects page</a> for more details on things I've worked on.
    </p>

    <h2 class="section-header">Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>
      For feedback, suggestions, or any professional queries, please reach out:
    </p>
    <ul class="contact-list">
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:miguelmota.contacts@gmail.com">miguelmota.contacts@gmail.com</a></li>
      <li>GitLab: <a href="https://gitlab.com/miguel_mota" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@miguel_mota</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
